<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
    <title>SwiftRoute - Optimize Your Delivery Logistics</title> <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700;800&display=swap"/>
    <style>
        body { font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; }
        /* Add any custom styles if needed */
    </style>
</head>
<body class="bg-gray-50 text-gray-800">

    <header class="bg-white shadow-sm sticky top-0 z-40">
        <div class="container mx-auto px-6 py-4 flex justify-between items-center">
            <a href="/" class="text-2xl font-bold text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-700">SwiftRoute</a>
            <nav class="hidden md:flex space-x-6">
                <a class="text-gray-600 hover:text-blue-600" href="#features">Features</a>
                <a class="text-gray-600 hover:text-blue-600" href="#pricing">Pricing</a>
                <a class="text-gray-600 hover:text-blue-600" href="/login">Login</a>
                <a class="bg-blue-600 hover:bg-blue-700 text-white font-medium py-2 px-4 rounded-md transition text-sm" href="/register">Get Started</a>
            </nav>
            <button class="md:hidden p-2 text-gray-600 hover:text-blue-600" aria-label="Open Menu">
                 <svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M4 6h16M4 12h16m-7 6h7"></path></svg>
            </button>
        </div>
    </header>

    <section class="bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-50 to-purple-100">
        <div class="container mx-auto px-6 pt-16 pb-20 md:pt-24 md:pb-28 flex flex-col lg:flex-row items-center">
            <div class="w-full lg:w-1/2 text-center lg:text-left mb-10 lg:mb-0 lg:pr-10">
                <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-extrabold text-gray-900 mb-4 leading-tight">
                    Deliver Smarter,<br /> Not Harder.
                </h1>
                <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-gray-600 mb-8 max-w-xl mx-auto lg:mx-0">
                    SwiftRoute provides intelligent route optimization and seamless inventory management to streamline your logistics, reduce costs, and delight your customers.
                </p>
                <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row justify-center lg:justify-start gap-4">
                    <a href="/register" class="bg-blue-600 hover:bg-blue-700 text-white font-bold py-3 px-8 rounded-lg transition duration-200 text-center text-lg">
                        Start Free Trial
                    </a>
                     <a href="#features" class="bg-white hover:bg-gray-100 text-blue-600 font-semibold py-3 px-8 rounded-lg transition duration-200 border border-gray-300 text-center text-lg">
                        Learn More
                    </a>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="w-full lg:w-1/2">
                 <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1604782286058-5f0109b54f7a?crop=entropy&cs=tinysrgb&fit=max&fm=jpg&ixid=MnwyODE1MDl8MHwxfGFsbHx8fHx8fHx8fDE2MjYxOTI0Mzk&ixlib=rb-1.2.1&q=80&w=1080" alt="Delivery van on a map" class="w-full rounded-lg shadow-xl object-cover" />
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section id="features" class="bg-white py-16 md:py-20">
        <div class="container mx-auto px-6">
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center text-gray-800 mb-12">Why Choose SwiftRoute?</h2>
            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
                <div class="text-center p-6">
                     <div class="bg-blue-100 text-blue-600 rounded-full w-16 h-16 flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
                          <svg class="w-8 h-8" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17.657 16.657L13.414 20.9a1.998 1.998 0 01-2.827 0l-4.244-4.243a8 8 0 1111.314 0z"></path><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 11a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z"></path></svg>
                    </div>
                    <h4 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">Optimized Routing</h4>
                    <p class="text-gray-600">
                        Generate the most efficient multi-stop routes using advanced algorithms, saving time and fuel costs daily.
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div class="text-center p-6">
                    <div class="bg-blue-100 text-blue-600 rounded-full w-16 h-16 flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
                          <svg class="w-8 h-8" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 11H5m14 0a2 2 0 012 2v6a2 2 0 01-2 2H5a2 2 0 01-2-2v-6a2 2 0 012-2m14 0V9a2 2 0 00-2-2M5 11V9a2 2 0 012-2m0 0V5a2 2 0 012-2h6a2 2 0 012 2v2M7 7h10"></path></svg>
                     </div>
                    <h4 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">Inventory Management</h4>
                    <p class="text-gray-600">
                        Track stock levels across multiple warehouses, manage items, and integrate inventory with your orders seamlessly.
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div class="text-center p-6">
                     <div class="bg-blue-100 text-blue-600 rounded-full w-16 h-16 flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
                          <svg class="w-8 h-8" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m5.618-4.016A11.955 11.955 0 0112 2.944a11.955 11.955 0 01-8.618 3.04A12.02 12.02 0 003 9c0 5.591 3.824 10.29 9 11.622 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.042-.133-2.052-.382-3.016z"></path></svg>
                     </div>
                    <h4 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">Visual Map Interface</h4>
                    <p class="text-gray-600">
                         Leverage interactive maps (powered by OpenStreetMap & Leaflet) to visualize routes, store locations, and delivery progress.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section id="pricing" class="bg-blue-600 py-16 md:py-20"> <div class="container mx-auto px-6 text-center">
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Ready to Streamline Your Deliveries?</h2>
            <p class="text-blue-100 mb-8 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
                Sign up for SwiftRoute today and take control of your logistics with optimized routes and efficient inventory management.
            </p>
            <a href="/register" class="bg-white text-blue-700 font-bold py-3 px-8 rounded-lg shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl hover:bg-gray-100 transition duration-200 text-lg">
                Get Started - It's Free! <%# Update text if pricing exists %>
            </a>
        </div>
    </section>

    <footer class="bg-gray-800 text-gray-400 py-8">
        <div class="container mx-auto text-center text-sm">
            <p>&copy; <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> SwiftRoute. All rights reserved.</p>
             </div>
    </footer>

    <%# Add JS for mobile menu toggle if needed %>

</body>
</html>